She frowned. " I an not a girlfriend. I am a female warrior." she 
smiled up at Repressor while on the comlink with HotRod. "I am busy 
at the lab." 
She closed her link and smiled at Repressor. She purred softly to 
him. "Where is Zardus. I need my orders."
